title: THIS IS YOUR LIFE -- guest Lou Costello ( also with Bud Abbott )
description:
This episode is from 1956, when their last movie together 
"Dance with Me Henry" came out.  Bud & Lou broke up their act
a year later due to losing money from their declining movie
popularly and problems with the IRS.  

Strangely enough their two TV series aren't even mentioned in this show!

In the last few years of Costello's life he had a better TV solo career 
as a guest star than Abbott did for his last 17 years.
